title: 2.4.4.3 - Additional Evidence from Other Technologies and Approaches
section 2_4_4_3

  |New technologies and approaches have emerged since {cite.1.'IPCC_2007 AR4} (Global Positioning System and radio occultation are discussed). However, these new technologies and approaches either constitute too short a record or are too immature to inform assessments of long-term trends at the present time.


  

